The easiest way is probably to open each array as a table with a separate `OPENJSON` call and join them by the generated key to match up the positions;

    DECLARE @json NVARCHAR(MAX) = N&#39;{
        &quot;car&quot;: [ &quot;Ford&quot;, &quot;BMW&quot;, &quot;Fiat&quot;],
        &quot;car owner&quot;: [&quot;Alex&quot;, &quot;Tom&quot;, &quot;Jane&quot;]
    }&#39;
       
    SELECT a.value car, b.value owner
    FROM OPENJSON(@json, &#39;$.car&#39;) a
    JOIN OPENJSON(@json, &#39;$.&quot;car owner&quot;&#39;) b
      ON a.&quot;key&quot; = b.&quot;key&quot;
    
This will give the result;

    car	    owner
    -------------
    Ford	Alex
    BMW	    Tom
    Fiat	Jane

